1. Install extensions:

# test_helpers
git clone https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/php-test-helpers.git
cd php-test-helpers
phpize
./configure
make
sudo make install

# runkit
git clone https://github.com/zenovich/runkit.git
cd runkit
phpize
./configure
make
sudo make install

2. Enable extensions:

# in php.ini:
extension=runkit.so
extension=test_helpers.so

This command should say two times enabled:

php -i | egrep 'runkit support|test_helpers support'
